MCP Server = a system where our own tools (functions. APIs) are exposed to AI so AI can perform task automatically.

Our tools, AI decides how to use it.

MCP Architecture (simple):
User → AI (ChatGPT / Agent) → MCP Server → Tool → Result → AI → User    

Components:
User
AI/Agent
MCP server
Tools

MCP = expose tools
AI = uses tools
No control logic by developer


MCP RESOURCES:
Resource is a live data view that AI can read directly.

example:
instead of calling list_unread_emails

AI can just read:
gmail://inbox


